description: Attackers mounted at least three separate strikes near the Red Sea resort of Eilat on Thursday. The Israeli military said the attacks originated in Gaza.
title: Deadly Attacks on Israelis Near Egypt
title_page: Deadly Attacks on Israelis Near Egypt - The New York Times
maintext:
Slide 1 of 11,
Armed infiltrators who Israel said had sneaked into the country through the porous Sinai border with Egypt attacked multiple targets around the popular Red Sea resort of Eilat on Thursday, killing at least seven Israelis and wounding 40. Wounded Israeli soldiers were treated at the site of one of the attacks.
